<plot>Two wounded American soldiers hide under mad Yeong-jin's barn. His sister, Yeong-hie, convinces Yeong-jin not to tell the North Korean soldiers in the area and takes it upon herself to heal them. They are discovered by Ki-ho, a communist supporter in the village who is in love with Yeong-hie. He uses this information to trap her into marrying him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?045330</url></doc>
